    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/5853b7a03ff08693f3b589bb9aaf4676.poster.avif?t=1770840544\" width=1170 height=304 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/5853b7a03ff08693f3b589bb9aaf4676.webm?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/5853b7a03ff08693f3b589bb9aaf4676.mp4?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nightmare Within</strong> 是一款第一人称心理恐怖游戏，恐惧源自主人公的内心。那座从童年到青年时期都无比熟悉的房子，正逐渐失去逻辑：灯光行为异常，物品仿佛获得生命，过去不断渗入现在。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏注重氛围营造、心理张力，以及通过环境展开的叙事方式。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>玩法</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索场景，与物品互动，解开富有氛围感的谜题。每一次行动都会揭示故事的片段，而世界也会随着主人公的感知而发生变化。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家通过观察细节、解读所见所闻，自行拼凑事件真相，逐步理解角色的内心世界。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/53d4a65f49efb74af0ab29147989c3e7.poster.avif?t=1770840544\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/53d4a65f49efb74af0ab29147989c3e7.webm?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/53d4a65f49efb74af0ab29147989c3e7.mp4?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>特色</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以剧情和氛围为核心的第一人称心理恐怖体验</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >动态变化的场景与环境元素</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无战斗、无武器的极简玩法</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过环境、光影与声音进行叙事</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >多种结局，取决于你的行为与对世界的理解</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/6f01af8b999c5f0d2fe35329b4713694.poster.avif?t=1770840544\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/6f01af8b999c5f0d2fe35329b4713694.webm?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/6f01af8b999c5f0d2fe35329b4713694.mp4?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>剧情</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你将扮演一名因失去而支离破碎的男人：先是失去了女儿，随后又失去了妻子。每一间房间都承载着他无法忘却的回忆、悔恨与画面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在探索过程中，你会发现笔记和记忆碎片，听到幽灵般的低语，并遇到那些将过去与现在交织在一起的物品。真相逐渐浮现，玩家一步步拼凑出主人公及其家庭的故事，意识到现实与内心世界之间的界限几乎已经消失。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/acd4d05a8f991e576c7a1f2e71f908cb.poster.avif?t=1770840544\" width=800 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/acd4d05a8f991e576c7a1f2e71f908cb.webm?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3061950/extras/acd4d05a8f991e576c7a1f2e71f908cb.mp4?t=1770840544\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
